Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.76,0:21:53.85,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}秘密　做了些好事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:22:02.41,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但淚　點點滴落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.40,0:22:10.90,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}頭　迷迷糊糊
